41
00:02:22,972 --> 00:02:24,002
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa?</font>

42
00:02:24,002 --> 00:02:25,342
<font color=#FFFF00>Apakah kau menemukan sesuatu selain...</font>

43
00:02:25,572 --> 00:02:28,412
