863
00:57:40,144 --> 00:57:42,214
<font color=#FFFF00>Apakah persidangan banding Yoon Seon Woo digelar besok?</font>

864
00:57:42,284 --> 00:57:43,284
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya.</font>

865
00:57:44,244 --> 00:57:48,054
