885
00:58:44,144 --> 00:58:45,314
<font color=#FFFF00>Atau...</font>

886
00:58:46,944 --> 00:58:49,514
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa sebenarnya yang coba mereka lakukan?</font>

887
00:58:55,924 --> 00:58:58,894
